#. module: pms_satisfaction_survey
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:pms_satisfaction_survey.field_pms_property__satisfaction_survey_enabled
msgid ""
"If enabled, a satisfaction survey will be sent to the main folio partner "
"once every reservation in the folio is checked out."
msgstr ""
"Si se activa, se enviará una encuesta de satisfacción al cliente principal "
"del folio cuando se haga el checkout de todas las reservas del folio."

